Toronto Generators (formerly Paga Technologies) has been installing and servicing standby generators since 2002. When the power goes out, a standby generator comes on automatically, restoring power to your home, business or cottage. We proudly supported our many clients through the December 2013 ice storm, and have expanded in order to continue providing exceptional service to our growing customer base.

We pride ourselves on our exceptional customer service, and our staff have the knowledge, experience and training to answer all of your questions. We would be happy to provide you with a site visit and written quote free of charge, so please call us today! Our specialty is Generator Installation and Service!

profile:
Proseal Floors Garage & Epoxy Concrete Floor Coatings is Ontario's Largest Commercial & Industrial Concrete Flooring Company. Proseal Floors Serving Ontario since 1979

The largest floor coating contractors in GTA ( Toronto, Mississauga, Brampton) with over 30 years in business, Proseal Concrete Floor Care Systems Inc. protects over three million square feet of concrete every year. Our full-time professional installation crews are totally equipped to complete your job guaranteed to your satisfaction and on schedule. Never using contractors, Proseal warranties its finished work and highest quality products to give you many years of outstanding performance and durability.

From specifications to the final polish, Proseal offers complete turn-key services in floor upgrades that dramatically improve your floor’s appearance and safety. Appreciate the clear benefits of Proseal’s top-quality protection coatings:

- Transformed rough & worn concrete
- Eliminates concrete dusting
- Reduced maintenance & lighting costs
Conductive Coating Systems for Industrial Safety

Proseal Concrete Floor Care Systems helps make your industrial facility safer with conductive coating systems. Consult with our technicians about our conductive, non-sparking epoxy floor coatings that control static and reduce fire risk.

Book a demonstration to see how Proseal can improve the safety and durability of your industrial floors. Our trained technicians prepare a comprehensive analysis of your plant’s work surfaces with specific recommended applications.

Our professional installers do it all, always working within your time schedule to avoid interruption of your business routine.

Proseal Flooring Products & Services Toronto

Epoxy & Urethane Floor Coatings :
When it comes to sealing your concrete floors, Epoxy and urethane coatings are definitely your best bet. The sealants interact with the concrete slab in such a way that a hard surface is formed, making it 6 times stronger than normal concrete and impenetrable to various liquids.

Garage Floor Epoxy Coatings Toronto : Are you searching for Epoxy Garage Coatings and professional installer for your garage floor Coatings or commercial epoxy floor in the Greater Toronto Area? In a time not too long ago, garages were all the same: outbuildings that were storage areas for parked cars, with boring gray concrete or even dirty floor coatings. Today garages have taken a more prominent place in the design of homes, often built to house three vehicles, and more often than not attached to the home. Garages have graduated from simple storage areas, becoming organized shops or showrooms. Today every bit of attention that a homeowner pays to the decorating of the home is paid to the garage as well, right down to what goes on the concrete floor coatings.

Floor Maintenance Recommendations
MAINTENANCE FOR SPECIAL FLOORING SYSTEMS : All Proseal flooring requires regular maintenance to ensure good looks and long service. It’s normal for floor coatings to become worn out and defaced by abrasion. Dust is an abrasive to floor coatings and it is imperative to remove it to reduce abrasion. Regular washing and wax lubricates the floor against abrasion. Waxing is recommended but not a requirement.
name: Proseal Floors Garage & Epoxy Concrete Floor Coatings In Mississauga
